# SchoolMS - Environment Variables Template

## Database Configuration
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_USER=root
DB_PASS=1234
DB_NAME=schoolms

## Application Configuration
BASE_URL=/SchoolMS/
APP_ENV=development
APP_DEBUG=false

## Email Configuration (Future Use)
MAIL_HOST=smtp.mailtrap.io
MAIL_PORT=465
MAIL_USERNAME=your_username
MAIL_PASSWORD=your_password
MAIL_FROM=noreply@schoolms.local

## Session Configuration
SESSION_LIFETIME=120
SESSION_SECURE=false
SESSION_HTTPONLY=true

## File Upload Configuration
UPLOAD_MAX_SIZE=5242880
ALLOWED_EXTENSIONS=jpg,jpeg,png,pdf,doc,docx

## Timezone
APP_TIMEZONE=Asia/Kolkata

## Notes
# - DB_PASS: Leave empty if no password set
# - APP_ENV: Set to 'production' for live deployment
# - APP_DEBUG: Always set to false in production
# - SESSION_SECURE: Set to true if using HTTPS
# - BASE_URL: Must match your server's URL path
